lead_paragraph: Rosberg, the Formula One leader, took pole position in Sochi while his Mercedes teammate Lewis Hamilton was 10th after another car failure ended his qualifying session early.

headline.main: Nico Rosberg Wins Pole in Russian Grand Prix
